  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give a girl a bike: help her to go to school</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In rural areas of India more than 60% of children drop out of school after 5th grade. High schools are not available in rural villages and girls need to travel long distance to pursue higher education. A lack of transportation and infrastructure causes parents to drop their daughters out of school. Mann Deshi Foundation gives this opportunity to girls by providing a bicycle and fulfills their dream of going to school. The journey to school will become safer and faster than before.</narrative>
  </description>
